data.title: Mammootty - Wikipedia
data.meta_description:
Mammootty - Wikipedia - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Mammootty is an Indian actor who has worked predominantly in Malayalam films for over 50 years. Some key points:

- He made his debut in 1971 and his breakthrough role came in 1981, winning a state award for his performance in Ahimsa. 

- The 1980s saw him act in over 150 films, establishing himself as one of Malayalam cinema's leading stars, though he also had commercial failures. 

- He has won several awards including 3 National Film Awards, 7 Kerala State Film Awards, and 13 Filmfare Awards for his acting performances over his career.
